      <scopecontent id="aspace_7271587deb2202f5da6917dc30a4e985">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, job descriptions, minutes, notes and related materials documenting the Development Advisory Committee, deanship search committees, and other committees of the Yale School of Medicine.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
